```class Solution {
    public int shipWithinDays(int[] weights, int days) {
        int result = 0;
        int sum = 0;
        for (int weight : weights) {
            sum += weight;
            result = Math.max(result, sum / days);
            sum %= days;
        }
        return result;
    }
}
```

efficiency: HIGH
time complexity: O(n) (where n is the number of weights)
space complexity: O(1)
energy implications: LOW

